<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 20:07:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>最高领导人的继任竞选受到干扰。哈梅内伊之子陷入内战？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/supreme-leaders-succession-race-disrupted-son-of-khamenei-in-fray/articleshow/110281539.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110281539.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 63 岁的莱西是哈梅内伊的门下，在伊朗神权政体中晋升，被广泛认为是接替 85 岁哈梅内伊的主要候选人。莱西得到了哈梅内伊的坚定支持，而哈梅内伊在他之前就担任过伊朗总统。 1989 年伊斯兰共和国创始人阿亚图拉鲁霍拉·霍梅尼去世后成为最高领导人。但对莱西担任总统表现的批评已经引发了人们的疑问，即他是否是接替健康状况每况愈下的哈梅内伊的最佳人选。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 19:27:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/supreme-leaders-succession-race-disrupted-son-of-khamenei-in-fray/articleshow/110281539.cms</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体：“技术故障”导致直升机坠毁身亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/technical-failure-caused-copter-crash-killing-raisi-state-media/articleshow/110281525.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110281525.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据伊朗官方新闻媒体报道，63 岁的莱西和阿卜杜拉希安周日在一场因“技术故障”造成的直升机坠毁事故中丧生。他们在水坝项目落成后从伊朗与阿塞拜疆边境出发，乘坐的直升机在乔尔法市附近的山区坠毁。搜救队在雨雾中在崎岖的茂密森林地区搜寻了几个小时，才找到了坠机地点。无人生还。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 19:21:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/technical-failure-caused-copter-crash-killing-raisi-state-media/articleshow/110281525.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国秘书长古特雷斯对伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西在直升机失事中丧生表示“悲伤”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/un-chief-guterres-saddened-on-demise-of-iran-president-ebrahim-raisi-in-chopper-crash/articleshow/110281366.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110281366.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 18:54:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/un-chief-guterres-saddened-on-demise-of-iran-president-ebrahim-raisi-in-chopper-crash/articleshow/110281366.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国安理会对伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西保持沉默，以色列大使称这是耻辱</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unsc-observes-silence-for-iran-president-ebrahim-raisi-israel-ambassador-calls-it-disgrace/articleshow/110281267.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110281267.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;包括美国在内的联合国安理会成员周一默哀一分钟，悼念在直升机失事中丧生的伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西及其随行人员。联合国安理会默哀片刻，悼念大规模谋杀的伊朗总统拉伊西。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 18:38:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unsc-observes-silence-for-iran-president-ebrahim-raisi-israel-ambassador-calls-it-disgrace/articleshow/110281267.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国监督机构敦促对核材料盗窃保持“警惕”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/un-watchdog-urges-vigilance-against-nuclear-material-theft/articleshow/110279696.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110279696.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国核监督机构周一呼吁对核材料和其他放射性材料的贩运保持“警惕”，称在过去 30 年中记录了 4,200 多起盗窃或其他事件。去年，31 个国家报告了 168 起事件，“符合历史记录”。国际原子能机构（IAEA）表示。它补充说，其中六起“可能与贩运或恶意使用有关”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 16:24:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/un-watchdog-urges-vigilance-against-nuclear-material-theft/articleshow/110279696.cms</guid></item><item><title>刚果政变失败：三名“中央情报局特工”在戏剧性枪战中被捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/failed-coup-in-congo-3-cia-operatives-arrested-in-dramatic-shootout/articleshow/110272818.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110272818.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 10:53:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/failed-coup-in-congo-3-cia-operatives-arrested-in-dramatic-shootout/articleshow/110272818.cms</guid></item><item><title>赖智就职后中国警告台独是“死胡同”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/china-warns-after-lai-inauguration-that-taiwan-independence-is-dead-end/articleshow/110272071.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110272071.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着新总统赖清德宣誓就职，中国对台湾独立发出警告。北京声称台湾是其领土，并威胁采取军事行动。黎智英被中国称为“危险的分裂分子”。中国对美国国防企业实施制裁。中国外交部汪文斌警告台湾独立。微博屏蔽了与就职典礼相关的标签。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 10:43:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/china-warns-after-lai-inauguration-that-taiwan-independence-is-dead-end/articleshow/110272071.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰即将击败俄罗斯吗？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/is-ukraine-heading-for-a-defeat-against-russia/articleshow/110271456.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110271456.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着俄罗斯夺回地形，哈尔科夫附近的战斗愈演愈烈。尽管取得了进展，但由于协调问题，专家们对俄罗斯的突破表示怀疑。乌克兰军队在美国武器的支持下限制了前进。延迟的 60B 美元军事援助削弱了防御能力。没有和平谈判；随着俄罗斯炮兵的逼近，有可能进行更多轰炸。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 10:25:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/is-ukraine-heading-for-a-defeat-against-russia/articleshow/110271456.cms</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾敦促中国允许对有争议的南海浅滩进行审查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/philippines-urges-china-to-allow-scrutiny-of-disputed-south-china-sea-shoal/articleshow/110270895.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110270895.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;菲律宾周一挑战中国允许国际社会对黄岩岛进行审查，因为菲律宾指责北京破坏了黄岩岛的海洋环境。马尼拉和北京之间的南中国海海上紧张局势不断加剧。菲律宾指责中国使用高压水枪并阻碍通过有争议的浅滩和珊瑚礁的行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 10:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/philippines-urges-china-to-allow-scrutiny-of-disputed-south-china-sea-shoal/articleshow/110270895.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗“抵抗轴心”盟友哀悼莱西之死</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-allies-in-axis-of-resistance-mourn-raisis-death/articleshow/110270300.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110270300.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德黑兰证实总统易卜拉欣·莱西在直升机失事中丧生后，伊朗支持的针对以色列及其盟友的“抵抗轴”成员周一表示哀悼。巴勒斯坦激进组织哈马斯、黎巴嫩真主党运动、也门胡塞叛军、叙利亚政府和伊拉克武装团体都对周日莱西和其他八人的去世表示哀悼。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:52:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-allies-in-axis-of-resistance-mourn-raisis-death/articleshow/110270300.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗直升机失事：穆罕默德·莫赫贝尔被任命为临时总统，阿里·巴盖里·卡尼代理外交部长</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-helicopter-crash-mohammad-mokhber-appointed-as-interim-president-ali-bagheri-kani-as-acting-foreign-minister/articleshow/110268431.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110268431.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:01:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-helicopter-crash-mohammad-mokhber-appointed-as-interim-president-ali-bagheri-kani-as-acting-foreign-minister/articleshow/110268431.cms</guid></item><item><title>北京称台湾政治不会改变“一个中国”的“事实”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/beijing-says-taiwan-politics-dont-change-fact-there-is-one-china/articleshow/110268003.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110268003.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 08:44:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/beijing-says-taiwan-politics-dont-change-fact-there-is-one-china/articleshow/110268003.cms</guid></item><item><title>在反对派抗议中，尼泊尔总理赢得议会信任投票</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/amid-opposition-protests-nepal-pm-wins-parliamentary-vote-of-confidence/articleshow/110268850.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110268850.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尼泊尔总理周一赢得议会信任投票。反对派提出抗议，要求议会对其内政部长在从政前非法收受多家公司资金的指控进行调查。普什帕·卡迈勒·达哈尔（Pushpa Kamal Dahal）是位于中国和印度之间的喜马拉雅国家的前毛派叛乱首领。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:14:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/amid-opposition-protests-nepal-pm-wins-parliamentary-vote-of-confidence/articleshow/110268850.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国禁止流行的朝鲜宣传视频赞扬金正恩</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-bans-viral-north-korea-propaganda-video-praising-kim/articleshow/110268544.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110268544.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;韩国媒体监管机构禁止播放朝鲜宣传音乐视频，该视频崇拜领导人金正恩，称其为“友好的父亲”和“伟大的领导人”。这一决定是在审查了可能违反《国家安全法》和对心理战的担忧后做出的。该视频在多个社交媒体平台上疯传。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:12:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-bans-viral-north-korea-propaganda-video-praising-kim/articleshow/110268544.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯哀悼莱西之死，赞扬他“支持巴勒斯坦抵抗运动”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-mourns-raisi-death-hails-his-support-for-palestinian-resistance/articleshow/110265432.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110265432.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 07:16:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-mourns-raisi-death-hails-his-support-for-palestinian-resistance/articleshow/110265432.cms</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处：拉法已有近 80 万人流离失所</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unrwa-nearly-800000-now-displaced-from-rafah/articleshow/110262745.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110262745.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国巴勒斯坦难民机构近东救济工程处负责人周六在再次呼吁加强对加沙平民的保护、提供安全的人道主义准入以及最终实现停火。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 05:37:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unrwa-nearly-800000-now-displaced-from-rafah/articleshow/110262745.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗总统莱西去世：目前我们对坠毁直升机的了解</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-president-raisi-dead-what-we-know-so-far-about-the-helicopter-that-crashed/articleshow/110262914.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110262914.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 06:47:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-president-raisi-dead-what-we-know-so-far-about-the-helicopter-that-crashed/articleshow/110262914.cms</guid></item><item><title>易卜拉欣·莱西去世后，谁将成为伊朗下一任总统？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/who-will-be-irans-next-president-following-ebrahim-raisis-death/articleshow/110261643.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110261643.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;根据伊朗宪法，总统去世后，由第一副总统临时领导职务。他们必须与司法部长和议会议长一起在50天内举行新的总统选举。在这种情况下，临时领导人将是穆罕默德·莫赫贝尔（Mohammad Mokhber），他是伊斯兰革命卫队前军官，曾任管理伊斯兰共和国资产的捐赠基金负责人。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 04:59:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/who-will-be-irans-next-president-following-ebrahim-raisis-death/articleshow/110261643.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国对伊朗总统直升机事故“深表关切”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/china-deeply-concerned-over-iran-presidents-helicopter-accident/articleshow/110261202.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110261202.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国周一表示，对伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西的直升机在德黑兰官方媒体所说的事故中失踪后表示“深切关注”，并承诺为救援行动提供帮助。中央电视台援引北京外交部的话说：“中方对莱西总统乘坐的直升机硬着陆深表关切，祝愿莱西总统和机上机组人员安然无恙。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 04:32:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/china-deeply-concerned-over-iran-presidents-helicopter-accident/articleshow/110261202.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西在直升机失事中丧生：接下来会发生什么</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-president-ebrahim-raisi-dies-in-helicopter-crash-what-happens-next/articleshow/110260908.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110260908.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西和外交部长在大雾中穿越山区时，因直升机坠毁身亡。这架飞机还载有其他官员，消失在伊朗西北部的山区。此前，官方媒体报道称，虽然直升机已经找到，但机上人员“没有发现生命迹象”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 04:31:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-president-ebrahim-raisi-dies-in-helicopter-crash-what-happens-next/articleshow/110260908.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>